pd_0_com_0text: Hey, I'm new in town. My name's [PName]. What is there to do for fun around here?
pd_0_com_1text: You'll have to excuse me. I have trouble ignoring such alluring people.
pd_0_com_2text: Hey, I'm... I mean, uhh, you'll... never mind.
pd_1_com_0text: Nothing I'd want to do with you.
pd_2_com_0text: I have noticed the nearby dungeons just off of the town.
pd_3_com_0text: Oh, you're STILL talking? I ssuppose I could set you alight, that could be pretty entertaining.
pd_4_com_0text: And I just can't resist drinking your blood if you keep talking. Go away.
pd_5_com_0text: You sound like a valuable ally. I could use your help exploring the dungeons if you'd assist me?
pd_6_com_0text: What's in it for me? You had better make it worth my while.
pd_7_com_0text: If the rumours are true, the monsters that dwell within them have even been posing a threat to the village.
pd_8_com_0text: If I see to it to venture into the dungeons would you be able to help me? It's dangerous to go alone after all.
pd_11_com_1text: Tell me something from your past
pd_11_com_2text: Tell me about your likes / dislikes
pd_13_com_0text: Could you tell me something about yourself?
pd_var_14_0: I used to bullsseye Giant Rats with my Elemental Sphere back home.
pd_var_14_1: Ssometimes I like to hide. away with a good tome...why are you looking at me like that? I'm allowed to read.
pd_var_14_2: Through my travels, I've found that you can create some pretty fasscinating potions from human blood...
pd_15_com_0text: How do you feel about us?
pd_17_com_0text: There's that word again, [PName]. Do not mistake this partnership for something more.
pd_18_com_0text: Our adventures thus far have been unexpectedly amusing. I like you, [PName]
pd_19_com_0text: I...trust you? This is not something I say lightly or easily, but I feel strongly attached to you, [PName].
pd_20_com_0text: Where are you from? What brought you here?
pd_21_com_0text: That is none of your concern.
pd_22_com_0text: My feet brought me here, but again where I come from does not concern you.
pd_23_com_0text: I have been travelling for a long time. It has been years since I gazed upon my homeland. If I find my purpose, I'll let you know.
pd_24_com_0text: I left my home as soon as I was able. I never felt at ease in Yuan-Ti society, I yearned for knowledge and the outsside world. I've lost track of how many years it has been, but I do not wish to return.
pd_25_com_0text: What do you like? What do you hate?
pd_var_26_0: My favourite colour is red, like the blood of my enemies, or your blood, specifically.
pd_var_26_1: Nothing beats a fresh egg. stolen from the nest of a Blood Hawk. And maybe the Blood Hawk itself, if I'm feeling peckish.
pd_var_26_2: Vegetables were a mistake. Why do humans consume them with such frequency?
pd_27_com_0text: What can you tell me about your abilities?
pd_29_com_0text: Whatever it is, I don't need it.
pd_30_com_0text: But...where is all the blood? That's the best part.
pd_31_com_0text: Oh...what a preciouss artifact. The craftsman captured the likeness of Sseth competently.
pd_32_com_0text: I am disgusted that you'd even think I would want this.
pd_33_com_0text: Oh my...these shoes are perfection. Think of the damage these could cause.
pd_35_com_0text: Take thesse away [PName], before I wretch.
pd_37_com_0text: I can hear the souls trapped inside. The screaming is like music to my ears. I am grateful for this gift, [PName].
pd_38_com_0text: I suppose I am in need of a scale brushing. Thank you.
pd_42_com_0text: How about this? Whatever you find in the dungeon, you get to keep.
pd_42_com_1text: Sorry, I have nothing to offer you.
pd_44_com_0text: Well then, I suspect most of the loot will be mine. I'm Sheva, not that you asked....
pd_46_com_0text: I really enjoyed spending time with you. We sure make a great team.
pd_46_com_1text: Are you a sorcerer? Because your beauty is inate.
pd_49_com_0text: We have been through so much together now.
pd_49_com_1text: You and I are a natural crit, how about we take things to the next level?
pd_50_com_0text: You're alright. Keep bringing me gold, though.
pd_51_com_0text: I find you tolerable. And maybe ssomewhat charming.
pd_52_com_0text: I really feel like we get along famously.
pd_52_com_1text: You must be a rogue with high dexterity, because you've stolen my heart.
pd_53_com_0text: You fight well, I greatly underestimated you.
